  "3164400": {
    "name": "Cat Go: Tactical Defense Braw",
    "steam_appid": 3164400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/e9a88d77d963184342e754c8043706cd.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/e9a88d77d963184342e754c8043706cd.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱只是基本，策略才是关键！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Cats Go》是一款最多支持4人游玩的猫咪×塔防×射击×动作游戏！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猫咪们安装植物塔，展开激烈的防御作战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 制定策略，与伙伴合作，找出伪装成同伴的恶魔猫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■ 这不是普通的塔防游戏！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>【别被可爱欺骗！塔防动作的新境界】</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用猫咪亲手布置的植物塔守护村庄！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射击动作与塔防玩法的完美结合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><u>【支持1~4人游玩（多人/合作模式）】</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 和朋友一起制定策略，配置植物塔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 缺肉了？这时候就需要“朋友援助”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><u>【丰富地图与难度，无限挑战等你来战】</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗都有不同地图与新策略！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从新手到高手，尽情享受猫咪战略塔防的世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/7acf63819f040b08b9f244ce945df1f3.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/7acf63819f040b08b9f244ce945df1f3.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/be1fdb0cd0de0c1f2a052db0a25a0adc.poster.avif?t=1754736393\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/be1fdb0cd0de0c1f2a052db0a25a0adc.webm?t=1754736393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ <strong><u>单人模式</u></strong> 🐈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制定完美的策略，成为勇敢独立守护村庄的猫咪吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ <strong><u>多人模式 - 合作</u></strong>🐈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在线游戏与队友一起合作吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果肉资源不足，可以向队友借一点哦，应该没问题吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ <strong><u>多人模式 - 恶魔</u></strong> 🐈‍⬛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一只伪装成猫咪的恶魔潜伏在你的队伍中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔猫会设置陷阱、让植物昏迷，并偷偷妨碍队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果怀疑某人是恶魔猫，就投票将它赶出村庄吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/176b47ca4db76d7453967a5c6ffa1744.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/176b47ca4db76d7453967a5c6ffa1744.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/753e155e0062ccf8a97ea40414e274ca.poster.avif?t=1754736393\" width=800 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/753e155e0062ccf8a97ea40414e274ca.webm?t=1754736393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变异植物外形独特，但都非常适合猫咪！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑选你喜欢的植物，种植、用心培育，并让它们进化为强大的塔吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras/d4e238b87c1b62645a60ea3eee7021e3.avif?t=1754736393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164400/extras_big/d4e238b87c1b62645a60ea3eee7021e3.avif?t=1754736393 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在拥有丰富设计与多样难度的地图中游玩吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过策略性玩法，体验通关的成就感和乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
